FBIS3-10179 "drlat042_a_94005" FBIS-LAT-94-042 Document Type:Daily Report 3 March 1994 CARIBBEAN Cuba Energy Commission President Stresses Fuel Efficiency FL0303010094 Havana Radio Progreso Network in Spanish 1200 GMT 2 Mar 94 FL0303010094 Havana Radio Progreso Network Language: Spanish Article Type:BFN [Text] The need to attain higher energy efficiency levels was stressed in Sancti Spiritus by Joel Domenech, president of the National Energy Commission, during a meeting to assess the development of national energy sources. During 1993, Sancti Spiritus Province displayed an improvement in energy use: a reduction of over 8 kg per peso of fuel produced.
